It works perfectly with the Reality XP, you can download it here 
http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/5613243/Reality_XP_WX500_and_GNS_WAAS_for_FSX_by_DCrack_--_NEW

To use it instead of the default FSX GPS

1. Install properly Reality XP (Read DCrack Readme.txt)

3. open the 'PANEL.CFG' file in the Duke B60 Panel folder, by default
   C:\Program Files\Microsoft Games\Microsoft Flight Simulator X\SimObjects\Airplanes\Carenado Centurion T210\panel
   erase it, copy the following text and paste it before saving the new 'PANEL.CFG' file.
